author: The Spiffing Brit
description:
Europa Universalis 5 is released and I have been playing it for nearly 6 months and finally get to share my experiences with the world! This is the biggest strategy game release of the year. In the last video we started a game as the Hanseatic League! The Single most overpowered nation in all of EU5. Today I will show you how to make big money, make a big empire and how to become the worlds leading economic great power! 

You Can Purchase the game here: https://paradoxinteractive.i38e.net/6y4ovq
(Use code "Spiffing" At checkout)
(Might be cheaper than steam in your local currency)

So what is EU5, rather simply this game is a 4X grand strategy game set between 5 centuries of human history starting in the late medieval leading into things like the renaissance and era of exploration filled with colonisation and discovery.
